      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/59/1315",
      "text": [
        " اَلسَّفَرِ فَقَالَ «مِنْ حِينِ تُصَلِّي اَلْعَتَمَةَ إِلَى أَنْ يَنْفَجِرَ اَلصُّبْحُ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1315 - Sama'a ibn Mehran asked Abu al-Hasan the First (as) about the timing of the night prayer during travel.\nImam (as) said: \"From the time you perform the 'Atamah (Isha, the night prayer) until the break of dawn (Fajr).\""
        ]
      }
    },
